'''粗尾鼠負鼠屬'''（{{lang|la|''Thylamys''}}，<ref name=msw3>{{MSW3 Didelphimorphia | id = 10400161 | pages = 17-18}}</ref>白鼠負鼠），[[哺乳綱|哺乳綱]]的一屬，而與鼠負鼠屬（白鼠負鼠）同科的動物尚有林負鼠屬（安氏負鼠）、短尾負鼠屬（短尾負鼠）等之數種[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]。

==形態描述==
本屬物種的[[前上頜骨|前上頜骨]]是圓的而不是尖的。雌獸有[[育幼袋|育幼袋]]，而且其[[乳頭|乳頭]]在腹部排成對稱的兩排 <ref name = "Eisenberg">{{Cite book
  | last = Eisenberg | first = John Frederick | authorlink = 
  |author2=Redford, Kent Hubbard
   | title = Mammals of the Neotropics: The Central Neotropics: Ecuador, Peru, Bolivia, Brazil
  | publisher = <!-- [[University_of_Chicago_Press|University of Chicago Press]] -->[[芝加哥大學出版社|芝加哥大學出版社]] | year = 1999 | location = | pages = 624 
  | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=p2MDAzCeQQoC&source=gbs_navlinks_s | doi = | id = 
  | isbn = 978-0-226-19542-1}}</ref>。除''T. macrurus''以外，其餘物種皆以其尾部儲存脂肪<ref name = "MSA">{{Cite book | last = Gardner | first = Alfred L. | title = Mammals of South America: Marsupials, xenarthrans, shrews, and bats | publisher = [[芝加哥大學出版社|University of Chicago Press]] |year = 2008 | location = | pages = 669 
  | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=dbU3d7EUCm8C&source=gbs_navlinks_s | doi = | id = 
  | isbn = 0-226-28240-6}}</ref>，儘管可能這並不適7於所有同屬物種<ref name=Voss2003>{{cite journal |author1=Voss, R.S.  |author2=Jansa, S.A.  |lastauthoramp=yes | year = 2003 | title = Nonmolecular data and new IRBP sequences: separate and combined analyses of didelphine relationships with denser taxon sampling | journal = Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History | volume = 276 | url=http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/dspace/handle/2246/444 | pages = 1–82 | doi=10.1206/0003-0090(2003)276<0001:PSODMI>2.0.CO;2}}</ref>。

